Introduction

ONE TOP (원탑) is a six-member project boy group created through MBC's Hangout with Yoo. They released their first song, "Say Yes," on December 2, 2023, and made their official debut with a stage performance on Show! Music Core on December 9, 2023.

The group comprises JS (Yoo Jae-suk), HaHa, Old K (Kim Jong-min), Joo Woo-jae, Lee Yi-kyung, and Young K (Kang Young-hyun).heir debut performance on MBC's "Music Core" on December 9, 2023, received enthusiastic responses from viewers.
